persistence:FinderMethod._andromda_hibernate_query: SELECT poi FROM Poi poi where evaluate_earth_distance(:x, :y, poi.latitude, poi.longitude) <= :rayon
SELECT DISTINCT location FROM Location location WHERE location.neighborhood.id=:idNeighborhood

SELECT DISTINCT poi FROM Poi poi WHERE poi.latitude IS NOT NULL AND poi.longitude IS NOT NULL AND ( poi in (SELECT pack.poi FROM Product as pack WHERE pack.code = :codePack AND pack.poi is not null) OR poi in (SELECT sug.product.poi FROM Suggestion as sug WHERE sug.pack.code = :codePack AND sug.product.poi is not null) )
SELECT consomation FROM Sale AS sale JOIN sale.bOProducts AS boProduct JOIN boProduct.consumptions AS consomation WHERE sale.id = :idSale
FROM TicketType WHERE product.id = :idProduct and name = :name
SELECT consomation FROM Sale AS sale JOIN sale.bOProducts AS boProduct JOIN boProduct.consumptions AS consomation JOIN boProduct.product AS produit WHERE sale.id = :idSale and produit.id = :idProduct
FROM Suggestion WHERE pack.id = :idPack AND product.poi.name = :identifiantTag
FROM Suggestion WHERE pack.id = :idPack AND position = :position

SELECT boProduct FROM Buyer AS buyer JOIN buyer.sales AS sale JOIN sale.bOProducts AS boProduct JOIN boProduct.product AS product JOIN product.company AS company WHERE buyer.id = :idBuyer AND (sale.debut is null OR sale.debut < :dateConsomation) AND (sale.fin is null OR sale.fin > :dateConsomation) AND product.externalCode = :codeOffre AND company.id = :idCompany AND boProduct.consumptions.size < boProduct.nombreConsommationMax
FROM Suggestion WHERE pack.id = :idProduit AND required = true
FROM Suggestion WHERE pack.id = :idPack AND product.id = :idProduct
FROM DatePeriod WHERE product.id = :idProduct AND startDate <= :date AND :date <= endDate
FROM TicketType WHERE product.id = :idProduct and (startDate is null OR startDate <= current_date()) and (stopDate is null OR current_date() <= stopDate)
FROM Suggestion WHERE pack.id = :idPack AND product.xtype = 'TRANSPORT'
